  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. COU1 is the validation activity itself — the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Methodology follows the protocol detailed in the peer-reviewed validation framework described by Nagaraja et al. and cross-referenced against the statistical harmonization guidance indexed at https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ymeth.2024.03.003, which provides the basis for the E/uval < 1.96 acceptance threshold adopted here.",
