    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed the required gradation level. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is judged acceptable given the quasi-static in vivo loading environment and the conservative nature of the single-rate test protocol. All three QoIs satisfy both the percentage-difference and E/uval acceptance criteria. The overall credibility package supports the Medium assurance level required for a Class II device at Model Risk Level 3. Decision: Accepted.",
